ex:utteranceTextES2002a0 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a1 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a10 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Great ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a11 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Hi , I'm David and I'm supposed to be an industrial designer ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a12 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a13 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "And I'm Andrew and I'm uh our marketing"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a14 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um I'm Craig and I'm User Interface ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a15 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "expert ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a16 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Great ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a17 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay . [laugh] Um"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a18 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "so we're designing a new remote control and um "^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a19 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Oh I have to record who's here actually ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a2 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Right"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a20 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So that's David , Andrew and Craig , isn't it ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a21 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "And you all arrived on time ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a22 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um yeah so des uh [other] design a new remote control ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a23 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um , as you can see it's supposed to be original , trendy and user friendly ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a24 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um so that's kind of our our brief , as it were ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a25 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um and so there are three different stages to the design ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a26 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um I'm not really sure what what you guys have already received um in your emails ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a27 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "What did you get ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a28 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um , I just got the project announcement about what the project is [other] ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a29 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Mm-hmm ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a3 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[other] Um well this is the kick-off meeting for our our project ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a30 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Designing a remote control ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a31 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Mm-hmm ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a32 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "That's about it , didn't get anything else ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a33 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Mm-hmm . Yeah , that's that's it ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a34 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Is that what everybody got ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a35 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Yeah ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a36 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Did you get the same thing ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a37 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a38 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Yeah ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a39 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a4 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um [laugh] and um"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a40 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So we're gonna have like individual work and then a meeting about it ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a41 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "And repeat that process three times ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a42 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um and at this point we get try out the whiteboard over there ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a43 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a44 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[laugh] So uh you get to draw your favourite animal and sum up your favourite characteristics of it ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a45 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So who would like to go first ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a46 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I will go . That's fine ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a47 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Very good . [laugh]"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a48 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Alright . So "^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a49 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[other] [whistling]"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a5 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "this is just what we're gonna be doing over the next twenty five minutes ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a6 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Mm-hmm ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a7 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um so first of all , just to kind of make sure that we all know each other ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a8 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I'm Laura and I'm the project manager ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002a9 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[laugh] Do you want to introduce yourself again ?"^^xsd:string .

